{"tid":2439911,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"M$: ZeniMax收購已完成, Bethesda正式加入Xbox大家庭","createTime":"2021-03-09T14:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T08:58:12.000Z","uid":36509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"344022be1d00ab63d3be8b5394b6b8aa79757f8e","tid":2439911,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.xbox.com/en-us/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2021/03/BethesdaAndXbox_HERO.jpg?w=1776\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xbox.com%2Fen-us%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2021%2F03%2FBethesdaAndXbox_HERO.jpg%3Fw%3D1776&h=fbd76348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全文: <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2021/03/09/officially-welcoming-bethesda-to-the-xbox-family/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xbox.com%2Fen-us%2F2021%2F03%2F09%2Fofficially-welcoming-bethesda-to-the-xbox-family%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=25ca7966\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2021/03/09/officially-welcoming-bethesda-to-the-xbox-family/</a><br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n未來會有部份新作Xbox/PC獨佔<br />\n<blockquote> With the addition of the Bethesda creative teams, gamers should know that Xbox consoles, PC, and Game Pass will be the best place to experience new Bethesda games, including<span class=\"orange\"><strong> some new titles in the future that will be exclusive to Xbox and PC players</strong></span>.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本週會有更多Bethesda作品加入Xbox Game Pass陣容<br />\n<blockquote>We will have more to share about what&rsquo;s next for our teams later this year. In the meantime, to properly celebrate this special moment, <strong><span class=\"orange\">we are bringing additional Bethesda games into Xbox Game Pass later this week</span></strong>. Stay tuned for more details!</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f28b030025a0e137a5cd693fbf1808686d280be","tid":2439911,"uid":36509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1